item.title: How to add new items to a server [bandos]etc
item.dc:creator: @the1337legend the1337legend
item.description:
@the1337legend wrote:

try in the model forums, basically, ull get a download link, with gzipped files prob labelled anything undder 15000 , copy paste them into ur clients models folder, then hopefully u get INTS with them, go to ur clients class.8 and then add the INTS in their along with the other ints previously in there, when u log in, type “add model (the numbers under 15000 here) and it should say " model successfully added” if not then make sure ur only typing ADD MODEL ##### no :: or no “” or nuthin… but yh, ask for models in the models forums.
